{"id":599619,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/11/【立此存照】朝阳群众官方微信公众号开通/","date":"2018-11-15T09:33:55Z","modified":"2018-11-17T00:30:36Z","title":"【立此存照】“朝阳群众”官方微信公众号开通","content":"<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/640-4.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-599621\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/640-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"310\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/640-4.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/640-4-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/640-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/640-4-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>只要提着正义之剑攻击，再柔弱的手臂也会力大无穷。这句话来形容“朝阳群众”是最恰当不过的，因为每一名“朝阳群众”都充满了正义感和责任感。“朝阳群众”所关注的、所反映的线索是那些违反法律的行为，对这些侵犯公众和公民的人身权益和财产安全的人和事要敢于斗争，同时也要善于斗争。对紧急的、突发的情况，您第一时间拨打110报警，对那些线索类的可以通过“朝阳群众”APP或者“朝阳群众”官方公众号通报给警方。每个“朝阳群众”都带着自己的善意和行动砥砺前行，再微小的光芒汇聚起来就能拥有太阳的力量。平安社会的建设期待您的积极参与……</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU2NTc2MjM1NQ==&amp;mid=2247483660&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=51c660b5e0c37055ae864e02f68ea63f&amp;chksm=fcb78150cbc008467eb792c2c108004adb9ddf08f940d7ce7d37ff16fd4e126a1684f04233b6&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=1115VhporATqmhp01iU64Nmz#rd\">链接</a></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>中国数字空间 | <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E6%9C%9D%E9%98%B3%E7%BE%A4%E4%BC%97\">朝阳群众</a></p>\n<p><span id=\".E7.83.BD.E8.AF.9D.E4.B8.8D.E8.BF.9E.E7.AF.87.EF.BD.9C.E7.BD.91.E7.BB.9C.E4.B8.BE.E6.8A.A5.E5.A4.A7.E4.BC.9A.E7.9A.84.E8.A1.A8.E5.BD.B0.E5.90.8D.E5.8D.95.E9.87.8C.E5.92.8B.E6.B2.A1.E6.9C.89.E6.9C.9D.E9.98.B3.E5.8C.BA.E7.BE.A4.E4.BC.97.EF.BC.9F\" class=\"mw-headline\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/04/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E4%B8%BE%E6%8A%A5%E5%A4%A7%E4%BC%9A%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A8%E5%BD%B0%E5%90%8D%E5%8D%95%E9%87%8C%E5%92%8B%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%8